						               													<description>You are a witch in the stock market and you must use your magic and ingenuity to obtain more money than your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Witch Market is a no language dependent, family-friendly filler where players must buy or sell ingredients from the market at the most opportune times.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Buy: To take all the ingredients of the same color from the market for Free! You know... using magic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sell: Discard from your hand all the Ingredientes of the same color and get coins for them! This is how you win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The value of each sold Ingredient will be equal to the number of ingredients of the same type sold on the Market! So plan your sales wisely.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Get rewards for being one of the fastest sellers! Sometimes selling first is better than selling a lot, so time your sales to get coin rewards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But don't be greedy! At the end of the game, each ingredient that is still in your hand will subtract 2 coins! So try to take the necessary Ingredients and sell them in time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Witch Market is a game of 20 minutes, where each movement will modify the Market and the decisions of all the witches.&amp;#10;Can you be the wealthiest witch? Or will your greed win you over?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
